run mpv [filename]

If there's no video and
"[vo/vdpau] OSD bitmaps do not fit on a surface with the maximum supported size"

"Exiting... (Quit)
Inconsistency detected by ld.so: dl-close.c: 771: _dl_close: Assertion `map->l_init_called' failed!
"
shows up, run mpv -vo xv [filename]

This tells mpv to use the default (and most compatible) video driver for X.

stream http:// by running mpv "url"